Package sketchoutline.tool

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SketchOutline
    The main class for the tool.
    SketchOutlineFrame
    The Main GUI of the Sketch Outline Tool.
    ThreadedTreeMaker
    Implements TreeMaker using multi threading.
    TreeMaker
    This class is responsible for fetching and pre-processing code from the editor and calling the japa parser internally to generate a tree data structure which is accessed by the GUI.
    Visitor
    Implements a VoidVisitor which visits every node and emits them.
